---
title: Spiced Salmon & Lemon-Chive Yoghurt with Veggie Mash & Greens
description: Here’s a sure-fire way to spruce up any plate of veggies and mash, by serving it alongside a blushing salmon, drizzled in
a yoghurt that is scented with chives and lemon zest. It will bring out the hearty flavours of the carrot and potato mash
and harmonise with the seasoning that’s been cooked into the salmon.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

